{"title":"登王屋山","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":11,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"登王屋山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登王屋山，见愚公的后人正抬条石铺旅游登山之路……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向一个古老的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向一本很薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但很有重量的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向一种崇高的向往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，我攀登王屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连翘花耀金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像阳光一样醒目；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄槲树吐芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人生命的鼓舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有六旬老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有年轻夫妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正忙着抬石头铺路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日精峰铺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向月华峰铺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直铺向日月歇足处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要引来五湖四海客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登王屋山强身壮骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找一种悟性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得到一种满足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是来看老愚公挖山的呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的后人们分明在补山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，这也是一种继续，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是为让民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站上一种精神高度！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}